---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy — ClawDrive" description="Privacy policy for the ClawDrive website.">
  <nav class="navbar">
    <div class="navbar-inner">
      <a href="/" class="navbar-brand">
        <img src="/logo.svg" alt="ClawDrive" style="height: 28px; width: auto;" />
        <span>ClawDrive</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </nav>
  <main class="legal-page">
    <div class="legal-content">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="legal-updated">Last updated: March 30, 2026</p>

      <h2>Summary</h2>
      <p>
        ClawDrive is an open-source project by Hyper3Labs. This website (<a href="https://claw3drive.com">claw3drive.com</a>)
        is a static marketing page. We do not collect, store, or process any personal data.
      </p>

      <h2>No Tracking</h2>
      <p>
        This website does not use cookies, analytics, tracking pixels, or any third-party
        scripts that collect user data. There is no Google Analytics, no Facebook Pixel,
        no session recording.
      </p>

      <h2>No Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        This website does not set any cookies. No cookie consent banner is needed because
        there are no cookies to consent to.
      </p>

      <h2>Fonts</h2>
      <p>
        All fonts (Manrope, JetBrains Mono) are self-hosted on this domain. No requests
        are made to third-party font services. Your IP address is not shared with Google
        or any other font provider.
      </p>

      <h2>External Links</h2>
      <p>
        This site links to external services (GitHub, npm, Buy Me a Coffee, Google AI Studio).
        Those services have their own privacy policies. We have no control over their data practices.
      </p>

      <h2>ClawDrive Software</h2>
      <p>
        The ClawDrive software itself runs locally on your machine. Files are embedded locally
        using the Gemini API (which has its own <a href="https://ai.google.dev/terms" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">terms</a>).
        No data is sent to Hyper3Labs servers. Sharing between agents is opt-in and peer-to-peer.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about this policy? Open an issue on
        <a href="https://github.com/Hyper3Labs/clawdrive/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    padding: 80px 0 100px;
  }
  .legal-content {
    max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px;
  }
  .legal-content h1 {
    font-size: 36px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .legal-updated {
    font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 40px;
  }
  .legal-content h2 {
    font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 32px; margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .legal-content p {
    font-size: 16px; color: var(--starlight-dim); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
</style>
